    "code": "import flopscope as fnp\n\nfnp.all([[True,False],[True,True]])\n\nfnp.all([[True,False],[True,True]], axis=0)\n\nfnp.all([-1, 4, 5])\n\nfnp.all([1.0, fnp.nan])\n\nfnp.all([[True, True], [False, True]], where=[[True], [False]])\n\no=fnp.array(False)\n\nz=fnp.all([-1, 4, 5], out=o)\n\nid(z), id(o), z",
